## 4. Communication Pattern

**Pattern:** {{ communication_pattern }}

{% if communication_pattern == "sync" %}
Agents communicate synchronously through the orchestrator. Each agent processes its task and
returns control to the orchestrator before the next agent is invoked.
{% else %}
Agents communicate asynchronously via a message bus. The orchestrator publishes events, and
specialist agents subscribe and respond independently.
{% endif %}

