## 6. Success Criteria

1. All automated steps execute without manual intervention.
2. Human touchpoints fire only at designated checkpoints.
3. Audit trail captures every agent decision.
4. Fallback to human escalation functions within 30 seconds.
5. Agent throughput meets or exceeds current manual throughput.
